Class Sample

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.Sample

  • public class Sample
extends java.lang.Object
    Date: 23-11-2017 This class represents a sample of all the WiFiNetworks scanned at the same time , in the same location and by the same device. This sample contains all the WiFiNetworks in an ArrayList.
    Author:
    Kineret Ruth Nahary & Yakir Amar
